      <Placemark>
        <name>Garden Canggu by Pizza House</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AE5a_GxDItlSozSlEn0rFJHsEf-dT8gM1LzbqKh-WEsNmZ4qxRfjg9jIGpiG6m3LBEh-Ru7IxUFBMv7le_W6nuwWqq6lWF0txsAmJl4gabiruLx0kQWorh3S0Z5FCyozpruvcGcov8ta4R5YVympdy10Z702vskoxNoBchvC961X3bXkeSccAiepjpdDX0xGvMPmpKz8IeNgKyjwSAQbUBIovpAwSai_XswYm4uOrKaGycS5sta4D05Vy5u9ell2BA?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>他們家的pizza真的超讚！讓我們一行人讚不絕口，連續去吃了兩年！]]></description>
