      <Placemark>
        <name>Hotel Tugu Bali</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AE5a_GxihiumTIVrwgQJ5odv2QFWlQv_hLZ3rpx1HIYthrQFZZWzECCJLA-TYFqpauXASFA_DqYEQys5X6_1fWstf2wKbZtyWnhAPbIMvpsijv2fEawFgd7WUpFbe7YSF0Y5sNA2dUJLheoV4VmTc2zYfOmf0vyokeL4ZEPx4k4n7JonJVvB4V9-U3v10oIqZaMsPD39Oiv2SLOIaydiz-OyoR_mZ9kFokbsxmJjwFYTlM1ZJnIrVGJfrUSNaJk6qg?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>文化表演的用餐體驗。Klook優惠票券：https://affiliate.klook.com/redirect?aid=40584&aff_adid=772420&k_site=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.klook.com%2Fzh-TW%2Factivity%2F90526-dining-experience-hotel-tugu-bali%2F%3Fspm%3DSearchResult.SearchResult_LIST%26clickId%3Db101cc332d]]></description>
