        <name>BAKED. Pererenan</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AE5a_GzROV74KgOnTLejlDIibgyM26AoTRpvIVGYbFQ8iWIetFFi_eZmPpVcpCEiha9r0gDCvh0b1Eq8hd9sU3oTdCV8JbFby3TFtvyIhDFCAQvfn-OMfzBCXK4Ukby-mf8PcwD6yHuPrO-PyBJ-YA-9C5sFPjTygDLu6Rifu6CpisIiHZ3ZKDDz2_YpcO1-zWafhFCZK7nvkedBKBkMnAyxl5La_amF-J9NG19y3cg_xUFrBjiJmTXRjqKd9PZfjA?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>有點像是藍瓶的感覺，專業時髦的咖啡廳，點了一份招牌蛋土司<br>但我覺得還好，調味有點甜甜的我吃不習慣<br>空間舒適，挑高，白色，也是很熱門的店，可以來試試看<br><br>Nikki提供：https://vocus.cc/article/64785ee1fd8978000187e1e6]]></description>
