      <Placemark>
        <name>Cafe Coach</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AE5a_Gzao2NuCQOhbDAAgYvRN1VCSqQU8RnZJdnoBgWoiZM1r4cQY_6hR1kohBC0YfV2MDIu0EE1pk3sajMsSrnRcoraE7zSoKGsX7yG06SdySshyS2E0sAUl5nBuBWfz0hSz4Ftdm1Sv6BzIeYcXPNlXWoNxNYDQQAN6tXAA6pwV4Ay45ubJlSz7a70fTrxcApOiWeuU9zpkPLNIT3Cwzn0fPHgUalmMGo0fneuCEwabkNvngWTAl5dVwUYWC_-dw?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>可能是我這輩子吃到最好吃的蛋（笑）也是誤打誤撞，在Radiantly alive canggu教室對面，想說進來吃個早餐等上課，烤過的麵包斯一小角，沾著蛋吃，真的好好吃啊，調味很好，很香很嫩～我會想再回來吃的好吃！<br><br>Nikki提供：https://vocus.cc/article/64785ee1fd8978000187e1e6]]></description>
