      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>M. MASON Bar | Grill Canggu</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AE5a_GwxWDhihMJLppB-m7hFnmJ991_pZMS0LEEZYosC9l6bNEZWeTQxljE_BleKabyRmExDI09MZfzKBaAvU7O16WYCuVnkWq99sAPG6WnDyoscz0SAks9mg_XL3Oo-tQJBUixsaAGnZQEsVxoGsilIH9L1BQSSmKFTH8jHoisNz6zh17X4AsVsc_2vG3CJ_O8VgCGPE-K0IvvPrOFten0zib2p_JjQSi8qNlIsktlDzfF7lXGOvW5IAa-H4LkSmw?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>M.MASON 是一家現代澳洲風格的餐廳，位於 Canggu 熱鬧的街區。餐廳外觀被綠意盎然的植物包圍，內部設有開放式廚房與溫馨的燈光，營造出舒適的用餐氛圍。後院的庭院區在夜晚燈光點綴下，特別適合浪漫約會或與朋友聚餐。菜單以地中海風味為主，融合了當地新鮮食材，提供多樣化的選擇。]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1899-0288D1</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value><![CDATA[https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AE5a_GwxWDhihMJLppB-m7hFnmJ991_pZMS0LEEZYosC9l6bNEZWeTQxljE_BleKabyRmExDI09MZfzKBaAvU7O16WYCuVnkWq99sAPG6WnDyoscz0SAks9mg_XL3Oo-tQJBUixsaAGnZQEsVxoGsilIH9L1BQSSmKFTH8jHoisNz6zh17X4AsVsc_2vG3CJ_O8VgCGPE-K0IvvPrOFten0zib2p_JjQSi8qNlIsktlDzfF7lXGOvW5IAa-H4LkSmw?authuser=0&fife=s16383]]></value>
