      <Placemark>
        <name>Penny Lane</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AE5a_GwKUJgqxo5S3aOXZTZ366AT6GCT75y5sZC0fuyAL8KkckQ7J-FVnFKcdfTN_5YK_IYkZnsFybUawtSQ_VGiXICrfpsYJZCNOSvvKr9pANpvgQpdPRMS9w46SwWxl_pEFCsB-fA4bivfB6NWFsQA8fiFx-q-KSQ2WLoQFGLVfYTxqIHqcbNXDKzF4LPHAARzVaRV5dBlWZ-C_BnBb9wPC2mFjCvgJcECpYOngiZc7AoroIGmWNemf_Sen6gXCQ?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>網紅早午餐/咖啡廳<br>特色：<br><br>以復古英倫風裝潢聞名（靈感來自披頭四歌曲），粉紅色調與霓虹燈飾超適合拍照。<br><br>主打健康早午餐，推薦「紅絲絨鬆餅」、「黑松露炒蛋」和創意咖啡特調。<br><br>週末人潮多需排隊，建議平日前往。<br>亮點：Instagram 打卡聖地，氛圍輕鬆慵懶，適合朋友聚會。]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1899-0288D1</styleUrl>
