      <Placemark>
        <name>Nalu Bowls</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AE5a_Gw1idllo6zHjbtUGxmhiyCrYMybbpmw5Pj1mOjwJyb0Hey7hBPJuSdAlTQvQX4OmTfoc15CTFCYUp5q7e6hru1cmcOlXUp6-saiEwxivWCuK4rdSkK4_cLpwMveXVfdw8jnr9X7HcmZhBDMcVPwZlr7CVMe82zYC2jg0tMqDuD25Pd6ncBF7mov7mc72ezEVhjelX2ZZha0aEbUdwGaAOk4LNgPfN0gze7DSdtuPKxX3hexfCD2U2mkFJLo-g?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>健康輕食（夏威夷風果昔碗）<br>特色：<br><br>專營色彩繽紛的「Acai Bowl」，基底用冷凍水果打製，配料可選格蘭諾拉、新鮮水果、堅果醬等。<br><br>人氣口味如「Sunset Bowl」（芒果+火龍果）和「Uluwatu Bowl」（巴西莓+可可碎）。<br><br>分店遍佈峇里島，長谷店位於海灘附近，方便外帶。<br>亮點：衝浪後補充能量的首選，清涼消暑又健康。]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1899-0288D1</styleUrl>
